# SBO Planner Logic Rules

## Constants

Use existing constants: `STAT_KEYS`, `EQUIPPED_SLOTS`, `VALID_ITEM_SLOTS`, `VALID_ALLOCATION_MODES`, `VALID_DATA_QUALITY_MODES`.

## LocalStorage

All keys must use `sbo-rebirth-planner.` prefix (e.g. `sbo-rebirth-planner.builds.v1`, `sbo-rebirth-planner.form-draft.v1`).

## Formulas

Formula values live in `SBO_DATA.formulas` in data.js. Reference them from app.js; do not duplicate or hardcode formula constants.

## Browser Automation

Add `data-testid` to key buttons and inputs (e.g. `generate-btn`, `save-preset-btn`, `current-level`).

## Example

```javascript
// Good — references SBO_DATA
const defMult = data.formulas.defMultiplierBase + data.formulas.defMultiplierPerPoint * def;

// Bad — hardcoded formula
const defMult = 5 + 0.01 * def;
```
